title: GoPro HD HERO Camera: AT Showdown Teaser
description:
Shot 100% on the HD HERO® camera from GoPro.

Check out this teaser from the AT Showdown at the Cow Palace in San Francisco.  See the boys like Mike Montgomery and Greg Watts take the GoPro on massive hits made possible by Andrew Taylor.

Music: Insightful
